{"type": "article", "id": 58268, "title": "梦的化石", "description": "这些今敏早期的漫画作品，才真正奠定了他一生的创作生涯。——横田正夫（日本动画学会前会长）", "date": "2018-11-14T10:50:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 42274, "name": "今敏"}], "category": 3, "column": 29, "author": 589058, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 122, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181113174210eRA0pIWh5OfSL8so.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">作者简介：</h3><p>今 敏（1963-2010）：动画导演、漫画家。 1984 年，在就读武藏野美术大学时完成漫画处女作《虏》， 1985 年完成《雕刻》，获千叶彻弥漫画新人奖。 1990 年开始连载首部长篇漫画《海归线》。同年作为美术设计参加大友克洋监督的动画电影《老人Z》，踏上动画创作之路。</p><p>1997 年完成动画处女作《未麻的部屋》，受邀参加柏林影展，并在亚洲奇幻电影节上获奖。接着陆续完成动画《千年女优》《东京教父》《妄想代理人》《红辣椒》。《千年女优》入围奥斯卡动画长片奖，与《千与千寻》同获日本文化厅媒体艺术节动画奖，名列世界五十大动画。</p><h3>书籍摘录：</h3><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113173811AW9kuQedNmIraqFb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.510968\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113173812YLp3qnUNs5gDd49M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.496799\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113173813TAos9ZFw3DCVKyfP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498721\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113173814cYtoVmRnCsqh6JuO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498074\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113173814h9DsbTelvOo624SH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.512887\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811131738185HP7wQL4VoTCSrOg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.507712\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113173819xCwu8ZlGJvT2KQeR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.496154\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113173819n5QpvKA9hiBjRyFU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.510309\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113173820cl1VBRUzZM4oLWk5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.492347\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811131738217bFwRj84ilVtBS1e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.487867\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图为电影《红辣椒》剧照，来自：豆瓣</p>"}